* A ; should not be required before a %> it should be automatic (done)
* Need support for <%=
* Make tags customizable
* Isolate code
* Compile templates
* Support <% var foo = { label: %>...<% }; %> (parsed)
* Support <% var foo = [ %>...<% ]; %> (parsed)
* Support <% var foo = %>...<% ; %> (parsed)
* Support <% fn( %>...<% ); %> (parsed)
* Support <%= fn( %>...<% ); %>
* Find good syntax for filters and support filter flags (<%@h=foo%>?)
